<i>of pounds of dirt,</i>

30:13.135 --> 30:15.720
and not be detected.

30:15.814 --> 30:18.890
<i>- It was laid with
a makeshift railroad track,</i>

30:18.975 --> 30:24.404
atop which sat a kind
