30:41.506 --> 30:43.915
But he was eager to get out
of there as soon as possible.

30:44.000 --> 30:47.094
<i>♪ ♪</i>

30:47.253 --> 30:48.670
<i>- El Chapo gets the word</i>

30:48.763 --> 30:51.181
<i>that the tunnel is almost ready,</i>

