31:19.294 --> 31:22.787
on America's greatest
national holiday.

31:22.872 --> 31:24.873
<i>It didn't quite work that way.</i>

31:24.957 --> 31:28.135
<i>They couldn't pull it off
by Saturday, July 4th,</i>

31:28.219 --> 31:30.295
and so they had
to delay one week.

31:30.379 --> 31:33.974
<i>♪ ♪</i>

31:34.058 --> 31:36.635
<i>- El Chapo isn't able to give
