32:52.294 --> 32:53.878
<i>digging up the floor
of his cell.</i>

32:53.963 --> 32:55.213
<i>[banging]</i>

32:55.297 --> 32:57.891
<i>♪ ♪</i>

32:57.976 --> 32:59.059
<i>- It's at that point</i>

32:59.143 --> 33:01.052
<i>that Guzmán sits
