33:14.826 --> 33:16.243
<i>of privacy while he was bathing.</i>

33:16.327 --> 33:19.904
<i>- You can see him pacing back
and forth in the cell,</i>

33:19.989 --> 33:22.165
and then all of a sudden
walking into the shower,

33:22.250 --> 33:23.408
and then he's gone.

33:23.492 --> 33:25.577
<i>♪ ♪</i>

33:25.670 --> 33:30.832
<i>- Guzmán goes into a hole
