<i>18-wheel truck.</i>

34:42.905 --> 34:47.826
<i>♪ ♪</i>

34:47.910 --> 34:52.005
<i>The truck drives him two hours
from the town of Toluca,</i>

34:52.090 --> 34:54.999
<i>where Altiplano prison is,
