35:20.860 --> 35:22.527
<i>♪ ♪</i>

35:22.611 --> 35:24.454
<i>- And his plane spirits him away</i>

35:24.539 --> 35:27.541
from the Mexican flatlands

35:27.625 --> 35:32.036
<i>back to his home base
