35:53.893 --> 35:57.487
Nobody questioned
as to why that was happening.

35:57.646 --> 36:00.157
<i>So it's pretty remarkable,
but, really,</i>

36:00.241 --> 36:01.983
<i>expected at this point in time.</i>

