- Following this escape,
El Chapo attempts to resume

36:40.940 --> 36:44.868
his regular activities,
but now it's not as easy.

36:44.952 --> 36:48.613
<i>This escape is
a significant embarrassment</i>

36:48.697 --> 36:52.200
<i>to the Mexican government,
who had, only a year before,</i>

36:52.284 --> 36:55.545
trumpeted his capture
as a major accomplishment

36:55.704 --> 36:58.215
in the nation's war
on drugs and crime.

36:58.374 --> 37:00.708
<i>That only adds fuel to the fire</i>

37:00.793 --> 37:04.387
<i>to try to see him
apprehended once again.</i>

37:04.546 --> 37:06.881
<i>- There doesn't seem to be
a prison in Mexico</i>

37:06.966 --> 37:10.143
<i>that can hold El Chapo for good.</i>

