<i>by escaping
through a mile-long tunnel</i>

37:31.991 --> 37:35.252
<i>under Altiplano prison.</i>

37:35.411 --> 37:37.829
<i>Embarrassed by their inability
to keep El Chapo</i>

37:37.922 --> 37:39.414
<i>under lock and key,</i>

37:39.498 --> 37:41.341
<i>the U.S. Drug
Enforcement Agency</i>

37:41.500 --> 37:43.668
<i>and the Mexican Marines</i>

