38:15.960 --> 38:19.629
<i>It was like being
in this live-action museum.</i>

38:19.788 --> 38:22.623
<i>There was this
overwhelming odor of gasoline,</i>

38:22.708 --> 38:24.459
<i>and the motorcycle
