<i>a tank of gasoline in it,</i>

38:26.295 --> 38:29.139
so it was just like El Chapo
had just been here,

38:29.223 --> 38:30.557
<i>and it gives me
goosebumps to think,</i>

38:30.716 --> 38:31.966
<i>just a few days before,</i>

38:32.051 --> 38:34.302
<i>the most notorious
drug trafficker in the world</i>

38:34.386 --> 38:35.887
<i>was standing right
where I was standing.</i>

38:35.971 --> 38:37.814
<i>♪ ♪</i>

38:37.973 --> 38:41.809
- After Guzmán's escape
from Altiplano,

38:41.902 --> 38:44.571
<i>the U.S.
law enforcement agents</i>

38:44.730 --> 38:46.397
<i>and the Mexican Marines,</i>

