<i>He carries
this mysticism to him,</i>

39:47.551 --> 39:49.719
almost this legendary status,

39:49.878 --> 39:52.806
because for so many years,
he was in hiding.

39:52.965 --> 39:56.309
<i>Everyone knew that this was
the man that was responsible</i>

39:56.468 --> 39:59.971
<i>for the violence in Mexico.
