41:02.543 --> 41:04.377
when he's brought
to the United States.

41:04.536 --> 41:05.795
[camera shutters clicking]

41:05.880 --> 41:08.789
[reporters whistle, shout]

41:08.874 --> 41:11.792
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

41:11.877 --> 41:13.470
<i>♪ ♪</i>

