<i>Given his history of escapes,</i>

41:19.968 --> 41:23.304
I wasn't entirely sure
that he would make it

41:23.388 --> 41:25.890
<i>until he actually landed
in New York City</i>

41:25.974 --> 41:28.485
<i>and I was there
in the courtroom with him.</i>

41:28.569 --> 41:30.478
<i>And even then,
there were moments.</i>

41:30.562 --> 41:31.821
<i>We were all in court one day,</i>

41:31.906 --> 41:33.731
<i>and all of a sudden,
